citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany the APHIS Official during the inspection process at 1:30 p.m.
on 07/11/2016. Phone calls were made to the numbers on file. A message was left and the licensee returned the
phone call. She was out of town and not available today to accompany the APHIS official during the inspection
process.
